ResumeParserData.Qualification: Completed B.Tech in Information Technology from SKP Engineering College (Anna university, Chennai) graduated with 72.3% in March 2012  Higher Secondary in Veveaham Higher Secondary School qualified with 83 % in March 2008  SSLC in Government High School qualified with 80 % in March 2006    PRODUCT PROFILE    Product Name : ESB (Enterprise Service Bus)  Product Type : WCF  Environment : C#, SQL, RIAK, Windows service	  Role : Product Support  Team Size : 2    Description	  The scope of this project is to authenticate service request and redirect to the actual system. It provides support REST and SOAP based requests.    Modules :   Gateway  Host Proxy  Host System  Gateway :   This component receives the request and authenticates the request by authentication tokens and redirects the request to the appropriate host proxy by reading the end point stored in database.  Components  1. Caching  2. Message headers  3. Routing Repository  4. Authentication  Host Proxy :     Host proxies are dedicated to convert the requests received from gateway to appropriate formats supported by the host system and also it formats the response message needed by the consumer. This provides the flexibility to the service consumer to choose web service type.     Host System :    The actual business services are implemented in this module.    Product Name : Unicorn (Automation Testing Framework)  Product Type : Class Library  Environment : C#, SQL, Windows service  Tools Utilized : Selenium, Appium, White, PICT  Role : Programmer  Team Size : 4    Description	  The scope of his project is to ease the tester's job by providing this framework also it helps the manual tester's to make testing automated having basic knowledge in C#. This framework provides services to store their test data, test case in a structured manner by keeping those in database.    Combinatory Testing  PICT - A command line tool to generate multiple combinations of data for a given model.   This focuses on generating multiple combinations of test data for a given model. This helps in testing a scenario with multiple combinations of data.  Multi Browser Support  Supports browsers such as Chrome, Firefox, IE and Edge.     Product Name : SURIBET  Environment : ASP.NET5 with .NET Core, C#, ADO.NET, MSSQL, WCF, Angular  Role : Programmer  Team Size : 5  Description : Providing an environment to the users for betting and gambling online, includes	    	  Lotto, Skinfiri, Sport Betting, Virtual games. Live Match odds are consumed from third	    	  Party service  Sport Betting  Sport betting is for betting on the match which is in progress, betting is done in two different ways, Single and Combo bet.  Lotto  Six numbers will be chosen in a number series along with an alphabet (Series falls in between   0 - 32) .Users who chosen all six numbers, will be announced as JACKPOT Winner and an amount of    1 , 50 ,000 SRD will be credited in their respective accounts.  Finally an alphabet will be chosen. Users who has the same alphabet, will be given one more chance to play by providing 2 free betting slips.    Project Name : Betting Statistics  Environment : C#, XML, SQL Server  Role : Programmer  Team Size : 1  Description : This project is for collecting statistics related to match progressing statistics that includes match result , player assists, goals scored , under over statistics, missing players in team, penalties etc.,  This module helps users to examine results of previous matches before placing bet.    Product Name : iHMS-2020 (Hospital Management System)  Product Type : Web Application  Environment : ASP.NET Web Forms, ADO.NET, C#, .NET 4 , Entity Framework 4.0 , LINQ    Database -MS SQL server 2012 , Crystal Report  Role : Programmer  Team Size : 5    Package1 : Hospital management System  The usage of this site is to maintain the hospital functional data and	  encounters patient data to the database as well as medication details. Patient module encounters details such as patient history, Follow up examination, prescribed medication details, etc. In order to meet multiple department's requirement, template has been implemented where they can define their own set of questions and answer types. Following components are used for this project.    Modules :   Patient registration module  Appointment module  Clinical module  Electronic health record module  Diagnostic module   Ward management module  Material management module  Billing module  MRD module  Linen management module  File tracker  Feedback module  Employee roster module    Package2 : Dashboard  Dashboard is for visualizing the data in a single page with graphical structure. The dashboard makes data such a way that every user can understand without spending much effort on how application flows. It has been implemented for In and Out patient bill, Consultant collections, etc.    Package3 : Pharmacy  In order to provide more flexibility, the HMS project has been integrated with pharmacy where hospitals can use available materials in their pharmacy.    Package4 : Material Management   As each department in a hospital maintains its own pharmacy, it becomes very hard to maintain the stock, shortage of items. In order to avoid such a scenario, a main store has been implemented as MMP Store.    Package5 : Security  In this module, users can create their own roles depends upon their requirement and provide access to the roles.     Barcode and Patient ID card Integration  As per customer requirement, barcode and Patient ID card printing functionality has been implemented with this web application. It plays a vital role in diagnostic module and in billing.     Product Name : Keystone - Customer Registration  Environment : Windows Forms, C#, ADO.NET, MSSQL  Role : Programmer  Team Size : 1  Description : The scope of this project is generating keys which are used to activate the Packages, Modules available in the HMS (Above mentioned project) .  Some of the functionalities implemented are  Customer registration  Product key generation  Module key generation   Renewal of product and module key  Collecting Nearing expiry of package, module lists and Maintaining AMC

PRODUCT PROFILE

Product Name : ESB (Enterprise Service Bus) 
Product Type : WCF
Environment : C#, SQL, RIAK, Windows service	
Role : Product Support
Team Size : 2

Description	
The scope of this project is to authenticate service request and redirect to the actual system. It provides support REST and SOAP based requests.

Modules : 
Gateway
Host Proxy
Host System
Gateway : 
This component receives the request and authenticates the request by authentication tokens and redirects the request to the appropriate host proxy by reading the end point stored in database.
Components
1. Caching
2. Message headers
3. Routing Repository
4. Authentication
Host Proxy : 
  Host proxies are dedicated to convert the requests received from gateway to appropriate formats supported by the host system and also it formats the response message needed by the consumer. This provides the flexibility to the service consumer to choose web service type. 

Host System : 
 The actual business services are implemented in this module.

Role : Programmer
Team Size : 4

Description	
The scope of his project is to ease the tester's job by providing this framework also it helps the manual testers to make testing automated having basic knowledge in C#. This framework provides services to store their test data, test case in a structured manner by keeping those in database.

Combinatory Testing

Multi Browser Support

Product Name : SURIBET
Environment : ASP.NET5 with .NET Core, C#, ADO.NET, MSSQL, WCF, Angular
Role : Programmer
Team Size : 5
Description : Providing an environment to the users for betting and gambling online, includes	  
	  Lotto, Skinfiri, Sport Betting, Virtual games. Live Match odds are consumed from third	  
	  Party service
Sport Betting
Sport betting is for betting on the match which is in progress, betting is done in two different ways, Single and Combo bet.
Lotto
Six numbers will be chosen in a number series along with an alphabet (Series falls in between 
0 - 32) .Users who chosen all six numbers, will be announced as JACKPOT Winner and an amount of  
1 , 50 ,000 SRD will be credited in their respective accounts.
Finally an alphabet will be chosen. Users who has the same alphabet, will be given one more chance to play by providing 2 free betting slips.

Project Name : Betting Statistics
Environment : C#, XML, SQL Server
Role : Programmer
Team Size : 1
Description : This project is for collecting statistics related to match progressing statistics that includes match result , player assists, goals scored , under over statistics, missing players in team, penalties etc.,
This module helps users to examine results of previous matches before placing bet.

Product Name : iHMS-2020 (Hospital Management System) 
Product Type : Web Application
Environment : ASP.NET Web Forms, ADO.NET, C#, .NET 4 , Entity Framework 4.0 , LINQ
  Database -MS SQL server 2012 , Crystal Report
Role : Programmer
Team Size : 5

Package1 : Hospital management System
The usage of this site is to maintain the hospital functional data and	  encounters patient data to the database as well as medication details. Patient module encounters details such as patient history, Follow up examination, prescribed medication details, etc. In order to meet multiple department's requirement, template has been implemented where they can define their own set of questions and answer types. Following components are used for this project.

Modules : 
Patient registration module
Appointment module
Clinical module
Electronic health record module
Diagnostic module 
Ward management module
Material management module
Billing module
MRD module
Linen management module
File tracker
Feedback module
Employee roster module

Package2 : Dashboard
Dashboard is for visualizing the data in a single page with graphical structure. The dashboard makes data such a way that every user can understand without spending much effort on how application flows. It has been implemented for In and Out patient bill, Consultant collections, etc.

Package3 : Pharmacy
In order to provide more flexibility, the HMS project has been integrated with pharmacy where hospitals can use available materials in their pharmacy.

Package4 : Material Management 
As each department in a hospital maintains its own pharmacy, it becomes very hard to maintain the stock, shortage of items. In order to avoid such a scenario, a main store has been implemented as MMP Store.

Package5 : Security
In this module, users can create their own roles depends upon their requirement and provide access to the roles. 

Barcode and Patient ID card Integration
As per customer requirement, barcode and Patient ID card printing functionality has been implemented with this web application. It plays a vital role in diagnostic module and in billing. 

Product Name : Keystone - Customer Registration
Environment : Windows Forms, C#, ADO.NET, MSSQL
Role : Programmer
Team Size : 1
Description : The scope of this project is generating keys which are used to activate the Packages, Modules available in the HMS (Above mentioned project) .
Some of the functionalities implemented are
Customer registration
Product key generation
Module key generation 
Renewal of product and module key
Collecting Nearing expiry of package, module lists and Maintaining AMC
